{"tid":1535024,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"與民賤聯賞花賞月慶中秋","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:30:21.000Z","uid":206109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7282b876c3275253b7bfb2e1a88e1656540c5c4","tid":1535024,"uid":206109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"代友post<br />\n<br />\n相信呢排大家都身心俱疲，需要搵啲節目調劑一下，而咁岩又比我發現民建聯page中，有位係培僑中學畢業，叫穆家駿既民建聯灣仔支部委員，標榜住自己係90後既中學教師，任教通識、中國歷史同地理。<br />\n<br />\n前排好積極參與咁撐警聯盟，又送護目鏡去狗局度，<br />\n又講將有大型活動係灣仔舉行咁。<br />\n原來佢地所指既大型活動，喺係灣仔一棟叫茂蘿街7號既場地搞慶中秋活動，即係以前既動漫基地！<br />\n<br />\n我朋成日去個邊坐，個度有個空地長期開放比公眾。<br />\n不如我地參加下佢地個活動啦，又可以試下用激光筆點下燈！！ 咁難得既活動，手足麻煩幫我推爆佢啦！！ ！"},{"pid":"06ffcc813269a9bef587079ce91178785aa34c90","tid":1535024,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"628667d282b3c6ed60ee07d904ea98c309125923","tid":1535024,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:30:21.000Z","